<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA83">
<l>kuṟaiyāka veñcoṟkaḷ kūṟiṉēṉ kūṟi</l>
<l>maṟaiyāṅ keṉavuraitta mālai – yiṟaiyēṉu</l>
<l>mīyuṅko leṉṟē yiruntē ṉeṉaippakalu</l>
<l>māyaṉkaṭ ceṉṟa varam</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As [I felt] a lack, I spoke harsh words. Speaking</l>
<l>about Māl, who is said, by the Veda, [to be] thus, I sat</l>
<l>however many days, thinking ‘will he give, even if it is little,</l> 
<l>the boon that goes [back] to the Dark one?’</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
